Maintainer: Ciarán Murray <cjm@niva-dk.dk>
Description: This package implements calculations of AZTI’s Marine Biotic Index  _AMBI_, as well as the Shannon Diversity Index _H'_ and the Danish benthic fauna quality index _DKI_. _Borja, A., J. Franco, V. Pérez, 2000. A marine biotic index to establish the ecological quality of soft bottom benthos within European estuarine and coastal environments Marine Pollution Bulletin 40(12): 1100-1114_.
